it seems its: weakness when handling "\\"causes two issues one being the execution of local chm files and the other is parsing of local htm pages stored in chm files which could be exploited using xss !
the poc i have given shows both of these issues i 'll try creating an exploit using xss and add it to my xploit page.

 

